videos.description: Alabama QB Tua Tagovailoa hits WR Jerry Jeudy for a 58-yard touchdown on the first drive of the game.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa throws strike for early Alabama TD

videos.description: Arkansas State punter Cody Grace mishandles the snap and gifts the Crimson Tide a 7-yard punt.
videos.headline: Botched punt gives Alabama great field position

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa connects with a wide-open DeVonta Smith for an easy 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa throws third TD pass of 1st quarter

videos.description: In his first series of the game, Alabama QB Jalen Hurts gets drilled at the 1-yard line and loses a fumble.
videos.headline: Hurts coughs it up at goal line

videos.description: Jalen Hurts links up with TE Irv Smith Jr. to make it 26-0 Alabama.
videos.headline: Hurts throws dart for 10-yd TD

videos.description: QB Jalen Hurts takes a big hit, but throws it on target to WR Jerry Jeudy for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Hurts stands tall to deliver TD pass

videos.description: Saivion Smith shows off his reflexes on an interception and runs it back 38 yards to the house for a Crimson Tide touchdown.
videos.headline: Alabama DB rips down INT for pick-6

videos.description: QB Justice Hansen finds WR Kendrick Edwards for a 23-yard touchdown pass, giving the Red Wolves their first score of the game.
videos.headline: Arkansas State gets on the board with 23-yd TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws his fourth touchdown pass of the game thanks to an impressive catch by Derek Kief.
videos.headline: Alabama WR keeps feet in for 14-yd TD

videos.description: Crimson Tide RB Najee Harris walks into the end zone for a 1-yard TD, giving Alabama a 50-point lead.
videos.headline: Alabama notches first rushing TD of game
